score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:35:30.000Z","msg":"多管齊下，佢地先識收"},{"pid":"c3b6e63cb8f5c3a87e4a1fd2acd5ef5898ba0881","tid":1319912,"uid":259493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:10:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"409ac4980d2938da33241e37301c15e32ab7c3e6","tid":1319912,"uid":273854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:29:52.000Z","msg":"唔得<br />\n警例只係比處長規管警隊<br />\n係for 警隊內部使用<br />\n大約等同運輸署嘅指引<br />\n冇直接法律效力<br />\n<br />\n可以睇下條文<br />\n入面冇講刑罰<br />\n<br />\n要告, 只可以<br />\n1. 刑事, 直接告個別警員刑事(傷人, 公務員行為失當)<br />\n2. 民事, 告處長管理警隊不善，賠錢或出禁制令(例如冇show id)"},{"pid":"4a317f5142c5f8e62d41954ea6956a5dfa9ce092","tid":1319912,"uid":300023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"聯署要求美國將警務處列為恐怖組織<br />\n<br />\n關於香港警務處由6月至今的對應和平集會遊行的暴力行動，並針對7月21日的元朗白衣人黑社會幫會恐怖襲擊、8月4日對被補少女的性暴力行為，以及一切濫捕白色恐暴行為，請協助聯署一份於美國白宮官網 &ldquo;We The People&rdquo; 的請願書，敦促美國政府將香港警務處列為恐怖組織。請按回複驗證郵件中的超連結來確認聯署。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=Nl%2Bce6%2FxXxAB2W4e8qnvdgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=a988e3ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n<br />\n希望值此聯署逼使美國及其他西方民主國家對該恐怖組織採取實質行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1419709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1419709</a>"}]}